name: Amsterdam
overview: Just when long-time couple Nadia and Martín begin to consider separating, an adorable stray dog finds his way into their home, and the two attempt to care for the animal together.

episodes.name: Amsterdam
episodes.overview: Long-time couple Nadia and Martín get ready to call it quits – until an adorable stray dog interrupts their plans.

episodes.name: The Same Old Fight (La pelea de siempre)
episodes.overview: After a financial blow, Nadia receives some promising career news, while Martín inadvertently works with her competition.

episodes.name: Fade Out
episodes.overview: After an unexpected fight brings Nadia and Martín closer than ever to breaking up, insecurities keep them from making things right.

episodes.name: An Empty Place (Un lugar vacío)
episodes.overview: After a painful but civilized separation, Nadia and Martín still can’t seem to agree on one small detail. To cheer Martín up, Cherny throws a party.

episodes.name: Shared Custody (Tenencia compartida)
episodes.overview: Martín decides to share custody of Amsterdam with Nadia, while everyone except Martín praises Nadia’s role in a new commercial.

episodes.name: Moving and Partying (Mudanza y fiesta)
episodes.overview: After moving in with Cherny, Martín hits a snag with Nadia in their shared custody of Amsterdam. Later, a hurt Nadia attends a party.

episodes.name: Separate Ways (Caminos separados)
episodes.overview: Martín and Nadia have separate, unexpected encounters and both forget Amsterdam.

episodes.name: Happy Birthday (Feliz cumpleaños)
episodes.overview: Lopez takes care of Amsterdam when Nadia spends a night out. Martín’s birthday gets complicated when Nadia discovers Marina is back in the picture.

episodes.name: Gochugaru
episodes.overview: Despite a perfect evening, Martín still misses Nadia. Then, when Amsterdam falls ill, Nadia and Martín reunite.
